===Pronunciation===
[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ˈlemən/

===Noun===
'''lemon''' ([[lemons]])

#a yellow [[citrus]] [[fruit]].
#a semitropical [[evergreen]] [[tree]] which bears lemons.
#a pale [[yellow]] [[color|colour]], the colour of lemons.
#the taste of lemons.
#(''slang'') an [[item]] that is [[defective]] or [[inadequate]].

